title: 'Totally worth it'
body: The shorts are absolutely as shown in the pictures, fitting is also as expected so don't go for a size bigger or smaller. The cloth material is very durable and soft and will last a while with proper usage. Color is also as shown in the picture and you can totally rely on that. From the view point of pricing i think it's a steal deal so just go for it.

title: 'Stitching Quality Poor & Rear Pockets TOO SMALL..'
body: The overall stitching Quality is POOR with dangling/loose threads at many places and stitches easily coming off. Also, the TWO REAR POCKETS are SO SMALL in size that the WALLET just FALLS OFF EASILY when you're seated, without one's knowledge...!! OVERALL NOT AT ALL HAPPY WITH THE QUALITY...

title: 'Good fit short at right knee length'
body: 'This is perfect fit short which is soft and light weight. The length is also perfect at knee level. Light weight makes us feel good but at the same time we may not feel it as great like real cargo ones. But over all it is comfortable and the price is also very good.'
